        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>Carles<add>?</add> Hotel</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>New York</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="align(right)"><date>Sept 1</date>.</p>
            <p>Dear Sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I arrived in<lb/> town yesterday, and<lb/> received your much<lb/>
                esteemed letter of the<lb/>
                <date>28</date> and our deeply<lb/> grateful for your<lb/> kindness. I
                telegraphed<lb/> you yesterday requesting</p>
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p>you to send me the<lb/> Ring to this address<lb/> by Express. I hope<lb/> you have
                received<lb/> the telegram and<lb/> will kindly send the<lb/> Ring as we leave<lb/>
                here on <del><date>Saturday</date></del><lb/>
                <date>Monday</date> morning.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Accept my sincere<lb/> thanks, and believe<lb/> me.</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">Yours respectfully</p>
            <p rend="indent(4)">
                <persName role="author">C. M. De La Mar</persName>
            </p>
            <p><addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee>.</p>
        </body>
